<title>Information</title>
<p class="title">Stage Play Information:</p>
<p class="para">Thou Shalt Not DIE ZERO_Kai (I got it wrong on the pic) is the first stage play released, and it's a prequel to the manga by 3 years.</p>
<p class="line"></p>
<p class="para">Thou Shalt Not DIE ZERO_Kai "Red End" and "Black End" are alternate endings to the prior stage play, with it being based on which one you went to.</p>
